{"tid":1966633,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[ViuTv 粵語韓劇星期一至五8:30-9:30]德魯納酒店","createTime":"2020-04-10T10:18:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T11:55:35.000Z","uid":189328,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6c19ede42a4766aa01c11ec493e6f1bf8c60cec0","tid":1966633,"uid":189328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T10:18:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">4月15日(星期三)8:30播</span></span><br />\n<br />\n劇情簡介<br />\n2019年，首爾市內變化最大的市中心正中間，位置於黃金寶地 &mdash; 明洞的古老破舊建築物，乍一看就像準備重建的空建築物，但仔細地看的話，其實是經營中的酒店。<br />\n<br />\n如果早上的話，在那前面有數百萬的流動人口經過，卻幾乎沒有客人進入那酒店裡面。而在開始入夜、路上變得更冷清、市中心也入睡之時，招牌便亮著燈光，酒店樓層亦會升高的....德魯納酒店。<br />\n<br />\n靈賓專用的德魯納酒店裡，超精英酒店管理人具燦星擔任著總經理，和乖戾、脾氣暴躁的社長張滿月一起，為特別的靈魂客人們提供特級服務時發生的故事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mpweekly.com/entertainment/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/screen-shot-2019-08-06-at-6.24.29-pm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpweekly.com%2Fentertainment%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2Fscreen-shot-2019-08-06-at-6.24.29-pm.png&h=6ff4c882&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca2a77768aefc45345b00e05e9626a7f3b148156","tid":1966633,"uid":313584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T10:46:13.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a648eb1b3e7e17c3db56cbfad69b1c51fd737c8","tid":1966633,"uid":44180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T12:28:03.000Z","msg":"留定名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab44365f8e6a6288f49c7bf95cd84be50a89f557","tid":1966633,"uid":319342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T12:38:18.000Z","msg":"我最愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1513f01c20ffc48aa377c198fe1c2b0a419fee4e","tid":1966633,"uid":197602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T12:39:15.000Z","msg":"睇過 不過都留名<img src